{"tid":1846943,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］你班仆街係咪唔要普選啦？DLLM","createTime":"2020-01-27T20:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T05:53:26.000Z","uid":326153,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"645f0f38f5e91d76e40b3816135a4327824f8b60","tid":1846943,"uid":326153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T20:06:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到底香港人有幾想要普選㗎DL!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二階段雖然可能好耐先會簽，但一日有呢個條款係度，美國都要高度注視，你唔L係唔簽呀？<br />\n<br />\n呼籲在中美第二階段協議加入落實香港真雙普選的承諾<br />\n剩4天，欠16000簽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=5a945fb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n<br />\n另外聯署機<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=b21f712b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a><br />\n有曬而家同香港示威相關嘅白宮聯署，加埋中文翻譯！<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！不能習慣不要懶<br />\n<br />\n**勤洗手戴口罩，保護自己<br />\n**祝大家平安渡過武炎疫情"},{"pid":"a6105300088ed64f46efaca42288e140ad423793","tid":1846943,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:03:56.000Z","msg":"P